---
title: Toasted Brown Rice Bowl with Green Beans, Carrots, and Cashews
description: Hearty brown rice, nuts, seeds, and veggies join forces for an energizing dinner of champions. Thanks to the addition of aromatics like soy sauce, ginger, and garlic, you’ll get a pop of umami flavor in every bite. Think of it as fried rice upgraded and filled out with ingredients that actually pop with veggie and protein-loaded goodness.
